  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "chapterTitle": "卷 上",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "29793610_13_4099-4325",
          "range": "4099-4325",
          "rangeStart": 4099,
          "rangeEnd": 4325,
          "markText": "古今之成大事业、大学问者，必经过三种之境界：“昨夜西风凋碧树。独上高楼，望尽天涯路”，此第一境也。“衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴”，此第二境也。“众里寻他千百度，回头蓦见，那人正在灯火阑珊处”，此第三境也。此等语皆非大词人不能道。然遽以此意解释诸词，恐为晏、欧诸公所不许也。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1738123890,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-01-29 12:11:30",
          "chapterUid": 13,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4099&rangeEnd=4325",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4099&rangeEnd=4325"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_3548-3573",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3548-3573",
      "markText": "人生只似风前絮，欢也零星，悲也零星，都作连江点点萍",
      "totalCount": 228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3548&rangeEnd=3573",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3548&rangeEnd=3573"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_7_2097-2168",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2097-2168",
      "markText": "而禅宗则将佛学和传统的儒家道家相融冥化，于是显示强大的生命力。外来文化只有和固有文化融契相化，才能保存势力扎下根来，并推动固有文化的改造和发展",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2097&rangeEnd=2168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2097&rangeEnd=2168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_10_1756-1784",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1756-1784",
      "markText": "社会上之习惯，杀许多之善人；文学上之习惯，杀许多之天才。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1756&rangeEnd=1784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1756&rangeEnd=1784"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_6007-6056",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6007-6056",
      "markText": "然而，那是一个政治时势、思想文化都极不宁静的时代，任何人都必须做出自己的选择。王国维最终选择了死。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6007&rangeEnd=6056",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6007&rangeEnd=6056"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_2218-2287",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2218-2287",
      "markText": "“感情上之疾病非以感情治之不可，必使其闲暇之时心有所寄而后能得以自遣。夫人之心力不寄于此则寄于彼，不寄于高尚之嗜好则卑劣之嗜好所不能免矣。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2218&rangeEnd=2287",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2218&rangeEnd=2287"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_3263-3361",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3263-3361",
      "markText": "词中的自然意象多是肃霜秋风，栖鸦孤雁、鹤唳乌啼、残霞落花，基本主题是人间无凭、人世难思量、人生苦局促。这种慨叹不是古人那种片刻失意落魄后的自怨自艾，而是词人王国维对宇宙人生一贯的哲学态度和艺术感觉",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3263&rangeEnd=3361",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3263&rangeEnd=3361"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_5801-5856",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5801-5856",
      "markText": "1927年6月，当北伐军进抵郑州，直逼北京时，王国维终于留下了“经此世变，义无再辱”的一纸遗书，投昆明湖自杀。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5801&rangeEnd=5856",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5801&rangeEnd=5856"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_6748-6764",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6748-6764",
      "markText": "人生过处唯存悔，知识增时只益疑。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6748&rangeEnd=6764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6748&rangeEnd=6764"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_13_2979-3141",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "2979-3141",
      "markText": "客观之诗人，不可不多阅世。[13]阅世愈深，则材料愈丰富，愈变化，《水浒》、《红楼梦》之作者是也。主观之诗人，不必多阅世。阅世愈浅，则性情愈真，李后主是也。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2979&rangeEnd=3141",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2979&rangeEnd=3141"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_3596-3611",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3596-3611",
      "markText": "最是人间留不住，朱颜辞镜花辞树",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3596&rangeEnd=3611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3596&rangeEnd=3611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_753-777",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "753-777",
      "markText": "王国维的一生，就是对人生问题不断追索讨问的过程。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793610&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=753&rangeEnd=777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4e43250071c69d4a4e4f426?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=753&rangeEnd=777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793610_6_5655-5689",
      "chapterUid": 6,
